comments: Brown (BOS) makes incidental contact with Irving's (BKN) hand after the release of his driving shot attempt.
As Horford (BOS) is going to set the screen, Griffin (BKN) briefly holds his arm but the contact is marginal and does not affect his positioning.
Brown (BOS) moves laterally into Durant's (BKN) path and delivers contact as he is dribbling up the floor.
Williams (BOS) moves alongside Durant's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during Durant's drive toward the rim.
Dragic (BKN) briefly holds Horford's (BOS) jersey as he is going to set the screen and the contact is marginal.
Griffin (BKN) moves into Smart's (BOS) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
As Brown (BOS) loses control of the ball, Durant (BKN) reaches in and makes marginal contact with his arm but he is able to regain possession.
Irving (BKN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Smart (BOS) during the shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) and Dragic (BKN) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound.
Smart (BOS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Durant (BKN), but as he dives for the loose ball, he initiates contact to Durant's legs that affect his SQBR.
Griffin (BKN) makes marginal contact with Smart (BOS) while contesting the shot attempt.
Mills (BKN) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Dragic (BKN) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
